## Why this is happening — 3 possible reasons

| Reason | What it means |
|---|---|
| LDAP groups not yet linked on `gitlab.sbi` | Groups exist in AD but haven't been synced/created on the new GitLab yet |
| Group names are different on `gitlab.sbi` | May have slightly different naming vs `gitlab.epay.sbi` |
| Your token lacks `read_api` on groups | Admin token needed to see all groups |

